=== Glycyrrhizin (Licorice Root)

Directly neutralizes HMGB1 — a DAMP released during cellular stress driving sterile inflammation. Probes whether HMGB1-mediated DAMP signaling contributes to PEM. *If glycyrrhizin reduces post-exertional HMGB1 and PEM:* HMGB1 is a causal PEM mediator. *CAUTION:* pseudoaldosteronism risk limits duration.

*Certainty*   Low to Medium.

*Level of action*   Partial root cause.